<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <title>Assistant Mail & Automatisation IA - Natalia</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Automatisez vos emails et workflows avec l'IA. Natalia traite vos demandes par email avec la même intelligence que par téléphone.">
  <%- include('./includes/_head.ejs') %>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex flex-col">
<%- include('./includes/_header.ejs') %>

<main class="flex-grow">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="section bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-primary/5 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="gradient-orb gradient-orb-1"></div>
    <div class="gradient-orb gradient-orb-2"></div>
    <div class="container-content relative z-10">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h1 class="hero-title text-h1-mobile md:text-h1 font-bold text-police-titre mb-4">
            <span class="text-gradient">Automatisez</span>
            vos emails et workflows
          </h1>
          <p class="hero-subtitle text-lg text-police-grey font-semibold mb-8">
            Natalia traite vos demandes par email avec la même intelligence que par téléphone. Catégorisation, réponse automatique, escalade.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-cta">
            <a href="./contact" class="btn btn-primary inline-flex items-center gap-2">
              Réserver une démo
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-image flex justify-center">
          <div class="relative animate-float-slow">
            <img src="../static/assets/images/businessDashboardPng2.png" alt="Assistant Mail IA" class="w-full max-w-lg rounded-xl shadow-lg glow">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem Section -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container-content">
      <h2 class="text-h2-mobile md:text-h2 font-bold text-police-titre text-center mb-12 animate-on-scroll">
        Vos défis avec <span class="text-gradient">les emails</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8" data-stagger>
        <div class="card border-l-4 border-l-red-500">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-red-100 text-red-600">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-2">Volume croissant</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">
            Des centaines d'emails par jour à trier, catégoriser et traiter. Vos équipes sont submergées.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card border-l-4 border-l-orange-500">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-orange-100 text-orange-600">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-2">Temps de réponse</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">
            Les clients attendent une réponse rapide. Les délais nuisent à la satisfaction et à l'image de marque.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card border-l-4 border-l-yellow-500">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-600">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 5a1 1 0 011-1h14a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V5zM4 13a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6zM16 13a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1h-2a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-2">Mauvais routage</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">
            Les emails arrivent au mauvais service. Les allers-retours internes rallongent les délais.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Solutions Section -->
  <section class="section bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container-content">
      <h2 class="text-h2-mobile md:text-h2 font-bold text-police-titre text-center mb-12 animate-on-scroll">
        Nos <span class="text-gradient">solutions</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6" data-stagger-scale>
        <div class="card text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow bg-white">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-2">Catégorisation auto</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">
            Natalia analyse chaque email et le catégorise automatiquement selon vos critères.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow bg-white">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-secondary/10 text-secondary">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 10h10a8 8 0 018 8v2M3 10l6 6m-6-6l6-6"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-2">Routage intelligent</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">
            Les emails sont dirigés vers le bon service, la bonne personne, dès leur réception.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow bg-white">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-600">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-2">Réponse automatique</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">
            Pour les demandes simples, Natalia génère et envoie une réponse personnalisée.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow bg-white">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-600">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-2">Création de tickets</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">
            Les demandes sont transformées en tickets dans votre outil de suivi (Jira, Zendesk...).
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Workflow Section -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container-content">
      <h2 class="text-h2-mobile md:text-h2 font-bold text-police-titre text-center mb-12 animate-on-scroll">
        Automatisation des <span class="text-gradient">workflows</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div data-stagger>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary text-white font-bold shadow-lg">
                1
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-1">Réception</h3>
                <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">L'email arrive dans votre boîte, Natalia l'analyse immédiatement.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary text-white font-bold shadow-lg">
                2
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-1">Analyse</h3>
                <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">Extraction du sujet, de l'intention, de l'urgence et des informations clés.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary text-white font-bold shadow-lg">
                3
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-1">Action</h3>
                <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">Réponse automatique, création de ticket, routage ou escalade selon les règles.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary text-white font-bold shadow-lg">
                4
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-police-titre mb-1">Suivi</h3>
                <p class="text-police-grey text-sm">Dashboard de suivi, métriques et amélioration continue des réponses.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 animate-on-scroll">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-police-titre mb-4">Intégrations</h3>
          <p class="text-police-grey mb-6">Natalia se connecte à vos outils existants :</p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-police-grey">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              Gmail / Outlook
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-police-grey">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              Jira / Zendesk
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-police-grey">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              Salesforce
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-police-grey">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              HubSpot
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-police-grey">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              Slack / Teams
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-police-grey">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              API personnalisée
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="section bg-gradient-animated text-white relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-white/5 rounded-full -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 animate-float"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-white/5 rounded-full translate-x-1/3 translate-y-1/3 animate-float" style="animation-delay: 2s;"></div>
    <div class="container-content text-center relative z-10">
      <h2 class="text-h2-mobile md:text-h2 font-bold mb-6 text-white animate-on-scroll">
        Automatisez vos emails dès aujourd'hui
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 text-white/90 animate-on-scroll">
        Réduisez de 60% le temps de traitement de vos emails avec Natalia.
      </p>
      <div class="animate-on-scroll">
        <a href="./contact" class="btn btn-white inline-flex items-center gap-2">
          Réserver une démo
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<%- include('./includes/_footer.ejs') %>

</body>
</html>
